name: Super Hero Match Game
description:
20 images (2 each of 10) were used to create this fun super hero matching game. This has been kid approved by my grandkids and kids of my friend. They loved them because they were easy to pick up and turn over. They are also small enough to travel with and to have a quick game for a restaurant wait. I love these because the game can be over quickly yet keeps the attention of kids of all ages.

The 1" game pieces were made using my good quality commercial button maker. These have a flat metal back with no magnet or pin attached. I've put the same color around the outside edge of each button so there's no "cheating."

Included with this game is a cotton drawstring pouch. 

These buttons are suitable for children age 4+. I would not recommend these for kids younger than 4.

Diameter: 1 inch (2.54 cm)

name: Nature Cufflinks - moose and elk - affordable and perfect
description:
Need a quick set of cufflinks that don't cost too much? This set is perfect! Featuring a moose and elk, these cufflinks are made with the same quality button materials as my magnets but I've attached a silver plated set of cufflink hardware.

Wonderful gift for your groom or groomsmen. Give each one their own individual set. The cufflinks are silver plated and the buttons have a piece of mylar covering the images to protect them.

Diameter: 1 inch (2.54 cm)

name: 100 wedding guestbook envelopes and card stock inserts
description:
100 mini wedding guestbook envelopes using a variety of papers and colorful card stock inserts make up this listing. The photos are stock photos of the types of paper I have available. 

**Please Note: Your envelope designs and card stock colors will be a surprise, but there will be a great variety!!

Perfect for business cards or a small note. 

**This listing INCLUDES the card stock inserts in a variety of colors.**

Need more or less than 100? No problem -- just contact me with your quantity and I'll adjust this listing for you.

Envelope size: 3 5/8" x 2 5/8" (9.2 cm x 6.7 cm)

Please note: You cannot use these envelopes to mail letters via the USPS. The minimum size the Post Office requires is a 3.5" x 5" size envelope.
